graph TD
    A[Start: Move Hatch] --> B{Open or Close?}
    B -- Open --> C[Attempt to Open Hatch]
    B -- Close --> D[Attempt to Close Hatch]
    C --> E{Open Successful?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Update Status: Open]
    E -- No --> G[Log Error: Cannot Open]
    D --> H{Close Successful?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Update Status: Closed]
    H -- No --> J[Log Error: Cannot Close]
    F --> K[Log Success: Hatch Opened]
    I --> L[Log Success: Hatch Closed]
    G --> M[Return: Failed]
    J --> M
    K --> N[Return: Success]
    L --> N
    N --> O[End: Complete]
    M --> P[End: Failed]